Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然问我这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那件事之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的四周似乎起了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我好像蛮有女人缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想校庆就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在扯什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没吃饭吧,陪我去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,怎么可能在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你从刚才就一直怪怪的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吃饭吧,吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个教授也待不久了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#13万人迷的五代?当心桃色电话!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你经常觉得有人在看你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,总是从背后来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是CIA?KGB?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是外星人? 也有可能是背后灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我当成神经病吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯着我看的人,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是一个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想说总有一天要去的 所以我慎重地保管着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是我对你的友情证明 拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是?阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别浪费我的友情喔,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有被女色冲昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七点以前,优待价1900
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股视线是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能陪我一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经注意你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,两个小时没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带一个男生到这种 寥无人烟的地方来,意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我已经有个心爱的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样我很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以让女人丢脸,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,只是接个吻的话,应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是刷子和油漆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们人手不足很伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为校庆就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有参加任何社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我已经注意你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找个好帮手来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫五代,来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,反正我很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是看板?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是背景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎新来的社员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长,他叫五代,是来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮忙的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦,你要加入人偶剧社啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你就加入吧 反正你很闲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入啦,我一个人好寂寞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的长相 真的很适合来玩人偶剧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增美好高兴喔,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,这是早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦 好痒喔,痒死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代好像跟女生混在一起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会这么认为?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他最近都很晚才回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在的女大学生都很爱玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代也习惯大学生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能比较有心情交女朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太 请不要把洋芋片吃得满地都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,居然把气出在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要把什么事 都跟五代扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是那个女孩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姓黑木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦请找五代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次那个女孩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是声音好像有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,五代吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,你好,上次很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,没有这种事 我玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,明天五点吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑木,到底怎么样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代家的这个管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个女人,而且年轻又美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,五代跟年轻女人同居?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是管理员啦,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是住在同一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,好像有好戏看了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姓神阪,麻烦找五代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,啊,神阪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?提早一个小时 那就是四点罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,嗯,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思,这么多电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,这也是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿过来,我拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,麻烦请找裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事神阪已经跟我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,都是我的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,因为这是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有很多女性朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是七尾,请找五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的,请你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话要跟我说?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用电话讲不太方便?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了,我现在就出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,今天好像都是我的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,因为这是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种气氛实在很不适合解释
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实,还会再打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,我们去咖啡店坐坐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不可以太奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只会叫我拿东西做白工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是进去喝点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要选圣代好呢? 还是布丁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果选特制圣代 两种都能吃得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃什么就点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太大声喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是新的女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他终于对管理员死心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接电话的那个女生是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次去看电影时 在路上碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?是她? 怎么差那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵,根本听不到了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你跟她 同住在一个屋檐下罗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么说也没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偶尔不会产生冲动吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会罗,一直都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是 她是个大美女,身材又好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在谈分手吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是男生的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛,干嘛,情侣吵架吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,那是五代哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是小孩能看的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被我看到一件大新闻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她讲响子的事,她就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是她察觉到我喜欢响子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这么喜欢我?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拿一下包包
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌,眼泪一直流个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很痛?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴隐形眼镜 有脏东西跑进去时会很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐形眼镜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,吓到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓…吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,你看,惣一郎 一半给你吃好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃就来追我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情侣吵架?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧看到的,我看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一点都不像平常的他 居然还去帮那个女生擦眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说,他们马上就和好罗 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有些地方很不坦率耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你是指什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过于封闭自己的话 男人会跑掉的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代跟谁交往都与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,吃了苹果再走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经没有果肉可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有果肉可以吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶都看见了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她该不会跟管理员说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么有趣的事 她怎么可能不说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈说是情侣吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情侣吵架?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我清纯的形象全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么清纯啊,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,过来借酒浇愁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑,这一切都是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑大婶有没有跟你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么,她如果没说就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什么都没跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员的反应如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎意料地蛮冷静的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很无趣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来换我上场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在? 对不起,我不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这些女孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉,抱歉抱歉,我不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神…神阪?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待会再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说,其实这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是增美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在一个人好寂寞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代哥哥,跟我一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这些女孩子… 不,刚才那个是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话听完的话 可不可以请你出去?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着,几天后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装了一个粉红色的公共电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉你的朋友 以后打这支电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,好像是我害的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,我以前就一直想说 得装支电话才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会有一些隐私 不想让别人听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有这回事 我没有什么不可告人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些打电话来的女生 跟我没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟谁有关系 都跟我无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么跟谁有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说,你真的误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底误会了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人真是不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 反正我是个死脑筋的寡妇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,你听我解释嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,站在这边听 简直就像是情侣吵架嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么误会嘛 有什么好解释的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到五代竟然是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定又是找五代的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不接呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我,请你不要挂断听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大学参加了一个社团
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些女生打来的电话 都是连络社团的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电话里哭的那个叫小泉 是个喝酒就会哭的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得很大声的叫神阪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人都是人偶剧社的社员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长是个男生,叫早乙女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常温柔和善的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,饭煮好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘,现在正精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我参加社团的事 应该早点跟你说才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于小津江在咖啡店哭泣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在…听吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来一刻馆 到下个星期刚好满一年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家说要开派对帮我庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:24:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回 “太好了五代!和响子首次约会”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,对不起 我居然同时答应约会和参加派对
